<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>header</title>
<style>
header{
		width: 100%;
		height: 60px;
		background-color: pink;
		text-align: center;
		line-height: 60px;
	}
header a {
    color: blue;       /* 링크 색상 */
    text-decoration: none; /* 밑줄 제거 */
    margin-left: 20px;     /* 왼쪽 여백 */
}
header a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline; /* 마우스 올리면 밑줄 */
}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<header>
	<h2>수행평가</h2>
    <a href="https://m.moviechart.co.kr/rank/realtime/index/image" target="_blank">요즘 유행하는 영화들</a>
</header>
</body>
